# Styling Conventions

## Dashboard Layout Styling

### Header Height

- Standard header height: `h-12` (3rem/48px)
- Use `shrink-0` to prevent flex shrinking
- Border: `border-b` for bottom border

### Content Structure

```tsx
<div className="space-y-6">
  {/* Page Header */}
  <div className="space-y-1">
    <h1 className="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">Page Title</h1>
    <p className="text-muted-foreground">Page description</p>
  </div>

  {/* Content sections with consistent spacing */}
</div>
```

### Grid Layouts

Standard responsive grid patterns:

```tsx
// Cards grid
<div className="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">

// Two column layout
<div className="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2">

// Four column metrics
<div className="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
```

## Sidebar Styling

### Background Colors

- Sidebar: `bg-background` (follows theme)
- Header/Footer: `bg-background` with `border-sidebar-border`
- Content: `bg-background`

### Border Patterns

- Sidebar: `border-r-0` (no right border, handled by SidebarInset)
- Header: `border-b border-sidebar-border`
- Footer: `border-t border-sidebar-border`

### Menu Item Styling

```tsx
// Use consistent button styling
<SidebarMenuButton className="rounded-sm">
  <Icon />
  <span>{title}</span>
  {badge && <SidebarMenuBadge>{badge}</SidebarMenuBadge>}
</SidebarMenuButton>
```

## Breadcrumb Styling

### Fragment Pattern

Use React fragments for conditional separators:

```tsx
{
  items.map((item, index) => (
    <>
      {index > 0 && <BreadcrumbSeparator />}
      <BreadcrumbItem>{/* breadcrumb content */}</BreadcrumbItem>
    </>
  ));
}
```

## Color System

### Text Colors

- Primary text: `text-foreground`
- Secondary text: `text-muted-foreground`
- Sidebar text: `text-sidebar-foreground`

### Background Colors

- Main background: `bg-background`
- Sidebar background: `bg-sidebar` or `bg-background`
- Card backgrounds: Default Card component styling

### Interactive States

- Hover: `hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground`
- Active: `bg-accent text-accent-foreground`
- Focus: Ring utilities from shadcn/ui components

## Responsive Utilities

### Common Breakpoints

- `md:` - 768px and up (tablet)
- `lg:` - 1024px and up (desktop)
- Default - mobile first

### Spacing Scale

- Page sections: `space-y-6`
- Related elements: `space-y-1` to `space-y-4`
- Component internal: `gap-2` to `gap-6`
